title: Meek Mill Interview
itunes:title: Meek Mill Interview
description:
Today on the show we had Meek Mill stop by where he spoke about his new album "Championships", still being on probation and more. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to the internet for putting out a prank and messing with Travis Scott and Kylie Jenner's relationship and Angela helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee".
